    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted driver\u2019s car featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and linear power delivery up to a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is robust, with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission providing tactile engagement. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains precise, offering the quintessential communicative steering rack feel. Presented in honest condition with a focus on mechanical longevity and performance integrity, this M3 is optimized for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
